Newly elected Limpopo ANC provincial chairperson, Stan Mathabatha, is vowing to unite and renew the party in that province. Courtesy #dstv403 POLOKWANE-Â Newly elected Limpopo ANC provincial chairperson, Stan Mathabatha, says he'll continue to work with those who contested against him, in order to unite and renew the ANC in the province. Mathabatha's slate registered a clean sweep during the election of the party's top officials in Limpopo on Saturday. Mathabatha says his leadership team will work towards improving governance and delivery of basic services.